The paper discusses a new attack on a secure key exchange system, which falls under the category of cryptography (cs.CR). The attack involves exploiting the transient behavior of the system, which also relates to information theory (cs.IT) and communication engineering (cs.CE). The paper also mentions the use of signal processing techniques (cs.MM) and the impact on network infrastructure (cs.NI).
